<subSubSection id="C31D6540FF95BD19FF35FC7CFAB0FB99" pageId="9" pageNumber="138" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BB836CBFF95BD19FF35FC7CFAB0FB99" blockId="9.[177,1383,727,1785]" pageId="9" pageNumber="138">
<emphasis id="B973EAD9FF95BD19FF35FC7CFE31FC4E" bold="true" box="[178,426,963,996]" pageId="9" pageNumber="138">Descriptive notes.</emphasis>
There are no specific measurements available. Mehely’s Blind Molerat has soft and moderately long fur. Most of dorsal surface is buff, and venter and head are grayish, with some reddish hues throughout. Diploid numberis 2n = 62.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
